<module>
    <h>sibh</h>
    <p><g>sibh</g>
        <en>you</en> is the second person plural <a href="?xx=nouns/personal_pronouns">personal
            pronoun</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-sbj">
            <h>subject</h>
            <p><g>sibh</g> can be used as the subject of a verb.</p>
            <p>Examples with <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a>
                <en>be</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>sibh</m> trang ag obair anns an achadh agus tha <m>sibh</m>
                            sgìth.</gd>
                        <tr>You are busy working in the field and you are tired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>sibh</m> aig an teine.</gd>
                        <tr>You are at the fire.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9 [226]</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>




</module>
